relationships.description: The client software is used to manage workspace groups.
Workspace groups can be located in specific regions, such as US West 2 (Oregon).
Workspace groups can use specific IP addresses in their firewall settings.
Workspace groups can be associated with specific KMSKeyIDs for data and backup buckets.
Workspace groups have metrics that provide performance and usage data.
Workspace groups have private connections for network communication.
Workspace groups enable network connections to workspaces.
